index 0000000..5cf34c5
--- /dev/null
+++ b/README-MashedD.md
@@ -0,0 +1,58 @@
+# opentdm
+
+# Notes/commands
+
+-
+
+# Building
+
+Tested on CachyOS.
+
+## Prerequisites
+
+Dependencies might be missing and some are Probably excessive.
+I didn't optimize this as it's time/cost not effective for me.
+Best might be to use Docker for the job.
+
+```bash
+sudo pacman -S cmake gcc
+
+# For cross compilation
+sudo pacman -S \
+    mingw-w64-tools \
+    mingw-w64-binutils \
+    mingw-w64-crt \
+    mingw-w64-gcc \
+    mingw-w64-headers \
+    mingw-w64-winpthreads
+paru -S \
+    mingw-w64-zlib \
+    mingw-w64-zlib-ng \
+    mingw-w64-ffmpeg \
+    mingw-w64-pkg-config \
+    mingw-w64-libpng \
+    mingw-w64-libjpeg-turbo \
+    mingw-w64-openal \
+    mingw-w64-zstd
+```
+
+## Compilation
+
+Review scripts before executing them.
+
+```bash
+./build-lin64.sh
+./clean.sh
+./build-win32.sh
+./clean.sh
+./build-win64.sh
+```
+
+# TODO
+
+- fork latest repo
+- apply changes in separate commits
+- add/change README.md
+- fix compilation warnings
+- get rid of `deps` folder
+
